reviewText: I had to clean all the cases and one of the dvds was broken.  I do love baby Einstein and so do the children.

look Im all for childrens dvds, but not 200 bucks !!
seems the creator of these DVD's has tasted the money and now wants MORE MORE MORE!
200 dollars for 26 dvds of 30min shows... NO THanks.. I'll stick to disney channel! IT'S FREE!
save your money.. this is nothing more than entertainment for your kids..

I have entire 26 DVD collection.
Play one of these DVDs, your baby will be staring at the TV. You can take a shower, vacuum or cook, you can finish anything you need to do.
